Where We Work

Ulfah Organization transcends geographical barriers to reach the epicenters of need in Syria, Palestine (Gaza), Nigeria, Yemen, Lebanon, and Afghanistan. Our holistic approach combines immediate relief with sustainable development.

Ulfah has made a tangible difference in Syria by providing urgent relief to those affected by conflicts, offering adequate shelter, and supporting education and orphan care. This has contributed to improving the lives of thousands of families and elevating the conditions of local communities.
